{"tid":753694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"筲箕灣女子企圖跳樓封路　交通受阻","createTime":"2018-07-23T23:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T23:53:36.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aec7a00342ae1952eb03907ba09bc78c13e5aafc","tid":753694,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:45:07.000Z","msg":"今日(24日)早上6時許，一名50餘歲女子，在筲箕灣東大街94-112號景峰大廈3樓至4樓平台危險位置企圖跳樓自殺，途人報警。消防趕至封路張開救生氣墊戒備，警方在場向女事主展開游說，雙方目前仍在對峙。 <br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，運輸署於早上6時56分宣布，筲箕灣東大街近東喜道全線封閉，交通受阻。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180724/mobile/bkn-20180724071434386-0724_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180724%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180724071434386-0724_00822_001.html&d=ZEvYQNGYBONbA6mLN9hUzMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=80496523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180724/mobile/bkn-20180724071434386-0724_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8d0f7ceb04a9207284b262dc6175473715b58d51","tid":753694,"uid":27458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:52:17.000Z","msg":"跳左未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b6dea2add2081ec178008fc1f594f29c50fbe5","tid":753694,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"死廢中阻人返工"},{"pid":"9b508b3f2d8d293109e2c2518e1aac9e25010942","tid":753694,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:53:36.000Z","msg":"唔好跳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}